Item Name: BUSHNELL SPOT ON 2 PACK (BLACK FRIDAY SPECIAL) TRAIL CAMERA
Web Item Name: Bushnell SpotOn Low Glow Trail Cameras 18MP 2/pk
Web Item Description:
The Bushnell Spot On 2-Pack Low Glow Trail Cameras are engineered for those passionate about wildlife hunting or property surveillance. These cameras bring advanced technology to the forefront offering low glow infrared illumination to capture high-quality images and videos of wildlife in their natural habitat without disturbing them. With a robust design these cameras are built to withstand harsh outdoor conditions making them ideal for year-round monitoring.

The pack includes two cameras doubling your coverage area and chances of capturing intriguing wildlife activity or ensuring the security of your property. Each camera is equipped with motion sensors that activate the camera to record when movement is detected ensuring you don't miss any action. The low glow LEDs provide sufficient illumination for clear nighttime imaging while remaining discreet.

These Bushnell trail cameras also feature long battery life reducing the need for frequent visits and maintenance in the field. They're easy to set up and mount with secure straps that can be attached to trees or posts. The cameras support SD cards for easy storage and transfer of images and videos.

  • Low Glow Infrared Technology: Ensures discreet nighttime imaging without disturbing wildlife.
  • Robust Outdoor Durability: Built to withstand harsh weather conditions for reliable year-round monitoring.
  • Motion Activated Sensors: Capture every movement with sensitive triggers and automatic recording.
  • Extended Battery Life: Minimizes maintenance with long-lasting performance in the field.
  • Easy Setup and Secure Mounting: Quick to deploy with secure straps for stable installation.

The SpotOn™ is built Bushnell® tough with 18MP image quality and speed that few can match for the money. The SpotOn™ runs on AA batteries and uses standard SD cards (sold separately). Slim in size makes this camera easy to keep hidden and stealthy. Grab a SpotOn™ and get your hunt on!

Keep your SD card in good condition by reformatting it regularly. This will erase all of your media so be sure to save it first.

Web Item Name: Alps Mountaineering Blaze 0 Regular Sleeping Bag 32x80 Charcoal/Orange
Web Item Description:
The Blaze series sleeping bags are constructed with a durable polyester ripstop shell with a soft polyester liner and are filled with synthetic TechLoft Silver insulation. TechLoft Silver insulation consists of multiple denier staple-length fibers that have a siliconized finish for maximum insulation loft and compactness. The Blaze uses two-layer off-set construction featuring a contoured hood and mummy shape which help seal in your warmth. For added heat retention the Blaze boasts an insulated chest and zipper baffle keeping the warmth in and the cold night air out. The Blaze is offered in multiple sizes and temperatures to accommodate most people. The Blaze is a great bag to add to your camping essentials.

  • TechLoft Silver insulation
  • Two-layer offset construction
  • #8 separating zippers
  • Insulated chest and zipper baffle
  • Polyester ripstop outer fabric
  • Polyester liner
  • Standard stuff sack

Web Item Name: Browning McKinley -30 Degree Sleeping Bag
Web Item Description:
The Browning Camping McKinley is a "heavy duty" oversized hooded rectangle sleeping bag. It uses a 2-layer offset construction to eliminate cold spots. The McKinley series use Techloft Insulation. Techloft Insulation consists of multi-hole staple-length micro-denier fibers that have a siliconized finish for maximum insulation loft and compactness.

It will keep you toasty on those colder nights when you'd prefer to have more "wiggle room" than you get with your mummy bag. This is a great hunting bag for those frigid nights when you want a good night's sleep.

Item Name: Alps Browning Strutter MC Country DNA Hunting Blind
Web Item Name: Alps Browning Strutter MC Camp Chair Mossy OakCountry DNA
Web Item Description:
The ultimate chair every turkey and predator hunter has been looking for is here—the Strutter and Strutter MC (More Comfort = Bigger Chair)! After years of tremendous success with the ALPS OutdoorZ Turkey Chair the one remaining feature hunters were asking us to try to solve was the "fold-up size." Web Item Description:
The CVA™ Carbon Fiber Paramount & Accura Collapsible Ramrod is a carbon fiber ramrod that makes reloading and cleaning your Paramount™ or Accura™ model muzzleloader a breeze especially at the range. The Paramount Ramrod is collapsible which makes for easy storage or packing in the field.

Item Name: WOLF V2 SS/EDGE 50Cal(ISM)Ambidex adj stockQRBP quick release breach plug
Web Item Name: CVA WOLF V2 SS/EDGE .50 Cal (ISM) Ambidextrous Adj Stock QRBP QR Breach Plug
Web Item Description:
The CVA Wolf V2™ Muzzleloader has many updated features including those that made the original Wolf the number one selling muzzleloader in the world. Still lightweight and easy to maneuver and is just the right size for youth or small-framed adults or even for the shooter who just wants a quick-handling gun for brush hunting. 

The Wolf V2 also features CVA’s QRBP (Quick-Release Breech Plug) – the only truly tool-free removal breech plug on the market today. Even after 20 or more shots the QRBP comes out with just a twist of the fingers – try that with any other "speed breech" system. Plus the break-action breech opens easily with just a touch of the breeching button which is located in the front of the trigger guard. The 100% ambidextrous stock comes in a Realtree® Edge™ camo finish. 

The reimagined stock design of the Wolf V2 makes this newest addition to the CVA line up even more comfortable to shoot. Now featuring a removable spacer in the stock the user can adjust the length of pull to match any shooters frame. Additionally CVA has gone away from the molded loops for the sling attachment in favor of metal sling swivel studs for a better experience.

The Wolf V2 features a compact and quick-pointing barrel that is made of stainless steel and is set up with a DuraSight® one piece scope mount.

Item Name: ACCURALR-X 50 CAL Cerakote Patriot Brown KonusPro 4-12x44 IR BDC Reticle
Web Item Name: CVA  ACCURA LR-X 50 CAL Muzzleloader Cerakote Patriot Brown KonusPro 4-12x44 IR BDC Reticle
Web Item Description:
The CVA™ Accura LR-X Scope Package comes with a 4-12x44mm bore-sighted Konus™ BDC IR scope and a durable CVA™ soft rifle case. The KonusPro® 275™ scope was designed especially for muzzleloaders helping to take the guesswork out of hold over angles for even the most difficult of shots. The exclusive ballistic reticle coinciding with the most popular black powder loads today provides you with a system of reference lines for exact aiming points from 75 to 275 yards. Lateral hash marks allow for precise leads of moving targets as well as compensating for strong crosswinds. The glass engraved ballistic reticle is unbreakable and the multi-coated optics are clear and bright.

The CVA® Accura LR-X™ Muzzleloader is an upgraded version of the Accura LR (Long Range). The Accura™ LR-X muzzleloader carries over most of the features from the previous model with some serious upgrades to the stock fit and finish and long-range terminal performance. The .50 Caliber Accura LR-X Muzzleloader is the ultimate rifle for hunters wanting long-range performance and accuracy with increased BC bullets and muzzle velocities.

The CVA™ Accura LR-X Long Range Muzzleloader features the new CVA X-Treme™ stock which sports an adjustable comb to fit any shooter and their optics of choice. This new comb adjustment is inset in the stock to allow for ambidextrous use as there is no protruding knob to worry about. Additionally the inset screw will allow for the gun to have a streamlined and sleek look and feel. This new CVA stock features Realtree™ Hillside Camo with a Soft-Touch™ finish for great grip in all conditions. Adjustable stocks are gaining popularity in the shooting community due to the ability to give a shooter a proper cheek weld to the stock whether they are using open sights or scopes with various ring heights.

The CVA Accura LR-X Rifle comes standard with the legendary Bergara™ barrel which features a Nitride coating as well as the added protection of CeraKote™ Patriot Brown on the exterior. The .50 caliber barrel on this muzzleloader is 30” long with a threaded muzzle to accept the new CVA™ Muzzle Brake which is threaded ¾” x 24. To properly stabilize the high BC muzzleloading bullets used in this muzzleloader the LR-X features a 1:28” twist rate. Borrowing technology from the Paramount this new Accura LR-X will offer a free-floated barrel without an under-barrel ramrod. Instead all new CVA Accura’s will ship with a carbon fiber collapsible ramrod.

The CVA Accura LR-X comes with a Quake™ Claw Rifle Sling Durasight® scope rail accessory kit Carbon fiber collapsible ramrod and CVA Owner’s Manual. As with any CVA Accura™ Muzzleloader there is an accuracy guarantee and a lifetime guarantee on manufacturer defects. If you have any questions about this muzzleloader please feel free to contact our friendly and knowledgeable customer service team! Also this gun is available on our custom packages page where you can choose your gun scope rings and case. We mount and bore sight all custom rifle combos!

**This package comes with one 15 pack of 330-grain PowerBelt ELR bullets

Item Name: ACCURALR-X 45 CAL Cerakote FDE KonusPro 4-12x44 IR BDC Reticle
Web Item Name: CVA ACCURA LR-X 45 CAL Muzzleloader Cerakote FDE KonusPro 4-12x44 IR BDC Reticle
Web Item Description:
The CVA™ Accura LR-X Scope Package comes with a KonusPro 4-12x44 bore-sighted KonusPro® scope and a durable CVA™ soft rifle case. The KonusPro® IR BDC Reticle scope was designed especially for muzzleloaders helping to take the guesswork out of hold over angles for even the most difficult of shots. The exclusive ballistic reticle coinciding with the most popular black powder loads today provides you with a system of reference lines for exact aiming points from 75 to 275 yards. Lateral hash marks allow for precise leads of moving targets as well as compensating for strong crosswinds. The glass engraved ballistic reticle is unbreakable and the multi-coated optics are clear and bright.

The CVA® Accura LR-X™ Muzzleloader is an upgraded version of the Accura LR (Long Range). The Accura™ LR-X muzzleloader carries over most of the features from the previous model with some serious upgrades to the stock fit and finish and long-range terminal performance. The .45 Caliber Accura LR-X Muzzleloader is the ultimate rifle for hunters wanting long-range performance and accuracy with increased BC bullets and muzzle velocities.

The CVA™ Accura LR-X Long Range Muzzleloader features the new CVA X-Treme™ stock which sports an adjustable comb to fit any shooter and their optics of choice. This new comb adjustment is inset in the stock to allow for ambidextrous use as there is no protruding knob to worry about. Additionally the inset screw will allow for the gun to have a streamlined and sleek look and feel. This new CVA stock features a Matte Black Soft-Touch™ stock for great grip in all conditions. Adjustable stocks are gaining popularity in the shooting community due to the ability to give a shooter a proper cheek weld to the stock whether they are using open sights or scopes with various ring heights.

The CVA Accura LR-X Rifle comes standard with the legendary Bergara™ barrel which features a Nitride coating as well as the added protection of CeraKote™ FDE on the exterior. The .45 caliber barrel on this muzzleloader is 30” long with a threaded muzzle to accept the new CVA™ Muzzle Brake which is threaded ¾” x 20. To properly stabilize the high BC muzzleloading bullets used in this muzzleloader the LR-X features a 1:22” twist rate. Borrowing technology from the Paramount this new Accura LR-X will offer a free-floated barrel without an under-barrel ramrod. Instead all new CVA Accura’s will ship with a carbon fiber collapsible ramrod.

The CVA Accura LR-X comes with a Quake™ Claw Rifle Sling Durasight® scope rail accessory kit carbon fiber collapsible ramrod and CVA Owner’s Manual. As with any CVA Accura™ Muzzleloader there is an accuracy guarantee and a lifetime guarantee on manufacturer defects. If you have any questions about this muzzleloader please feel free to contact our friendly and knowledgeable customer service team! Also this gun is available on our custom packages page where you can choose your gun scope rings and case. We mount and bore sight all custom rifle combos!

*This package comes with one 15 pack of 285-grain ELR bullets

**This model comes with a VariFlame ignition system.

Instead all new CVA Accura’s will ship with a carbon fiber collapsible ramrod.

The CVA Accura LR-X comes with a Quake™ Claw Rifle Sling Durasight® scope rail accessory kit carbon fiber collapsible ramrod and CVA Owner’s Manual. Also this gun is available on our custom packages page where you can choose your gun scope rings and case. We mount and bore sight all custom rifle combos!

Item Name: ACCURA MR-X 50 CAL MUZZLELOADER NORTHWEST - Cerakote Tungsten + Nitride WPS
Web Item Name: CVA ACCURA MR-X 50 cal Muzzleloader Northwest - Cerakote Tungsten + Nitride WPS
Web Item Description:
The CVA Accura MR-X .50 cal Northwest stands out as a top-tier mountain/rack muzzleloader with robust corrosion protection (Cerakote + Nitride) excellent build quality (Bergara barrel QR breech) and user-friendly comfort (adjustable comb light weight). It shoots accurately when loaded with matching sabots/bullets though you may need to experiment for best fit. The factory iron sights are good but many seasoned hunters prefer aftermarket options - just ensure compliance in your hunting area.

  • Caliber & Barrel: .50 Cal Magnum with a 26" fluted 416 stainless Bergara barrel 1:28 Twist
  • Finish: Barrel and receiver are dual-coated - internally Nitride-treated for corrosion resistance and externally Cerakote Tungsten for additional protection and style.
  • Stock: Ambidextrous soft-touch synthetic stock with adjustable X-Treme comb and Veil Alpine (or OD Green) camo designed for a precise cheek weld
  • Size: Weighs approximately 6.7–7.8lb (depending on configuration) with an overall length of ~41–44" 14.5" length of pull 
  • Ramrod: Carbon-fiber collapsible PalmSaver rod; no under-barrel ramrod to allow a free-floated barrel 
  • Sights & Mounts: Comes with Williams Rear Peep & Fiber Optic Front sights drilled/tapped for scope mounts (despite some regional restrictions)
  • Trigger: Fully adjustable from about 3 to 4.75 lbs pull weight 
  • Accessories: Includes CrushZone recoil pad Quake Claw sling
  • Mfg Lifetime warranty

The 'Northwest" designation ensures compliance with stricter regional regulations (e.g. Washington) such as:

  • Exposed ignition system using musket caps (musk cap ignition).

  • Open or peep sights instead of scopes.

  • Bann on sabots and electronic triggers—be sure to confirm your state’s exact requirements

Web Item Name: Diana Bandit Air Pistol .22 Cal 7 Pellets 630 fps Wood with Adjustable Sights
Web Item Description: Diana has been synonymous with quality German air guns since 1890. The Diana Bandit brings 130 years of heritage to market in an affordable Pre-Charged Pneumatic pistol. The Bandit features a rifled barrel with an integrated moderator adjustable sights and an 11mm dovetail for mounting optics a single-shot or 7-shot magazine option and a 50cc air cylinder which can be charged up to 2900 PSI. The rifled barrel provides excellent accuracy in this air pistol. The muzzle brake/moderator helps reduce the crack of the muzzle blast when shooting at higher velocities. Adjustable sights are ready to go out of the box but if you prefer to add an optic the receiver has an 11mm dovetail. With two options for loading the single-shot tray or the 7-shot rotary magazine the Bandit is ready for precision shooting or fast paced hunting. The 50cc air cylinder can be charged up to 2900 PSI of pressure. The smaller volume of the cylinder makes charging faster and easier. A muzzle velocity of 630 fps is attainable with .22 pellets. An ergonomic target style pistol grip and 2-stage Diana Improved Trigger will help you attain optimal accuracy. The Bandit is a great way to get into PCP air gun sports.

Web Item Name: Hatsan Zada Airgun Rifle .177 cal 1300fps Black
Web Item Description:
Hatsan’s ZADA break barrel rifle is an entry-level spring action air rifle. The refined design is precision-engineered to be the ultimate high-performance beginners shooting platform.

Designed for a lifetime of use the ZADA utilizes a steel rifled barrel and a synthetic molded shroud to reduce overall weight. The ZADA is available in three calibers .177 caliber .22 caliber and .25 caliber and is capable of producing up to 24 ft-lbs. of energy.

Hatsan focused on ease of use when equipping the ZADA with an easy-cocking break barrel purpose-built for the beginning shooter. Its large muzzle break with Hatsan’s QE technology with an integrated sound moderator makes manipulating the single shot cocking action smooth and nearly effortless. As a result this provides more control to the shooter and quieter shots down range.

The ZADA sports a new tactical style stock with a pistol grip designed to be more ergonomic and attractive than its predecessor. Its ambidextrous synthetic stock is rock solid and lightweight. Designed with a Monte Carlo cheek piece and rubber recoil pad the ZADA features comfort similar to those found on the most advanced Hatsan air rifles.

This airgun incorporates an integrated shock-absorbing advanced-polymer scope rail that will keep the included 4×32 Optima scope zeroed for superior accuracy. If you prefer not to use the scope the ZADA is fitted with contrasting colored fiber optic sights. The rear sight is fully adjustable for both windage and elevation. It boasts a fully adjustable trigger manual firing safety and an automatic cocking safety making the NEW ZADA a great entry-level airgun for those interested in picking up a fun hobby.

Web Item Name: Hatsan Zada Airgun Rifle .25 cal 750fps Black
Web Item Description:
Hatsan’s ZADA break barrel rifle is an entry-level spring action air rifle. The refined design is precision-engineered to be the ultimate high-performance beginners shooting platform.

Designed for a lifetime of use the ZADA utilizes a steel rifled barrel and a synthetic molded shroud to reduce overall weight. The ZADA is available in three calibers .177 caliber .22 caliber and .25 caliber and is capable of producing up to 24 ft-lbs. of energy.

Hatsan focused on ease of use when equipping the ZADA with an easy-cocking break barrel purpose-built for the beginning shooter. Its large muzzle break with Hatsan’s QE technology with an integrated sound moderator makes manipulating the single shot cocking action smooth and nearly effortless. As a result this provides more control to the shooter and quieter shots down range.

The ZADA sports a new tactical style stock with a pistol grip designed to be more ergonomic and attractive than its predecessor. Its ambidextrous synthetic stock is rock solid and lightweight. Designed with a Monte Carlo cheek piece and rubber recoil pad the ZADA features comfort similar to those found on the most advanced Hatsan air rifles.

This airgun incorporates an integrated shock-absorbing advanced-polymer scope rail that will keep the included 4×32 Optima scope zeroed for superior accuracy. If you prefer not to use the scope the ZADA is fitted with contrasting colored fiber optic sights. The rear sight is fully adjustable for both windage and elevation. It boasts a fully adjustable trigger manual firing safety and an automatic cocking safety making the NEW ZADA a great entry-level airgun for those interested in picking up a fun hobby.

Features:

  • Available in .177 caliber .22 caliber and .25 caliber
  • Ambidextrous synthetic tactical stock with pistol grip
  • Monte Carlo cheek rest
  • Rifled steel barrel
  • QuietEnergy fully shrouded barrel and integrated sound moderator
  • Includes 4×32 Optima scope and mounts
  • Checkering on grip and forearm for better control and feel
  • Rubber buttpad for recoil absorption
  • Accepts both 11mm dovetail and Weaver mounts
  • Adjustable trigger pull and trigger travel
  • Manual and automatic cocking safety
  • Anti-bear trap safety
  • Micro-adjustable rear sight for both windage and elevation with fiber optics
  • Large muzzle break for easy cocking

Web Item Name: Carbon Express Maxima Triad XSD 400 Hunting Arrows - 12/pk
Web Item Description: The Carbon Express® Maxima™ Triad™ is a Tri-Spine XSD (Extreme Small Diameter) .166 hunting arrow with performance at its core.   • Tri-Spine/RED ZONE Technology – Patented 3 spine arrow shaft with less than 1/3 the oscillation vs single spine arrow & FOUR TIMES the ACCURACY.

Web Item Name: Muzzy Bowfishing V2 Adjustable Compound Bow System - RH
Web Item Description:
The Muzzy® Bowfishing highly adjustable compound bow system custom is designed to adapt to the needs of a wide range of potential users.

Built for the demands of long days on the water with the versatility to accommodate shooters of all sizes and strength the new Muzzy Bowfishing V2 compound bowfishing bow comes as close to one size fits all as a bow can. A new and improved version of previous Muzzy compound bowfishing bow models the V2 features a redesigned aluminum riser with optimized geometry to enhance aiming improved grip for greater comfort and less torque and an upgraded cable guard and slide system for smother draw and extreme tunability.

Extra-long limb bolts serve to improve field adjustability letting users make in-the-field adjustments in draw length from 25-31.5- inches and draw weight from 25-55lbs without the use of a bow press or other complicated tools. Rugged easy drawing and user friendly the new 33.8-inch axle-to-axle V2 is prepared to meet and exceed the demands of even the most discriminating bowfishermen while staying concealed in a cloak of a new reptile-inspired custom camo pattern. Adding to the bows forgiveness are a generous 7.8-inch brace height and 70% let off for easy work during hours on the water or multiple draw situations.

Available as a bow only in right-and left-handed models.

Web Item Name: GlenDel Half-Scale Elk 3D Archery Target
Web Item Description:
Built by the brand who brought bowhunters the industry’s first 3-D archery target with a replaceable 4-sided core GlenDel® 3-D targets introduces the first-of-its-kind half scale elk.

Utilizing the field-proven design of GlenDel’s PolyFusion™ 4-sided core technology this anatomically-accurate archery target mimics the silhouette of one of North America’s largest big game animals — all without the size or expense of a life-sized version. Constructed of ultra-durable self-healing polyfoam and incorporating GlenDel’s exclusive 12”x12”x12” 4-sided core system the half scale elk combines easy arrow removal with exceptional target life in a manageable package. Purpose-built to enhance any backyard range the PolyFusion open layer foam construction used to build the core and vitals takes open layers of foam and fuses them to the target’s inner wall to increase durability and expand overall target life. With up to 5X the shooting surface three different vital views give bowhunters life-like aiming solutions at various shot angles while also to enhancing target durability. The half scale elk offers easy arrow removal and is built to withstand hours days weeks months and even years worth of shots from field points fixed and mechanical broadheads.

Though this easy-to-set-up target’s size has been proportionately reduced from its full-sized inspiration its features are anything by paired back. Sporting a large removable six-point rack the body size simulates a bull weighing approximately 300 pounds stands 38” inches tall at the shoulder and is the largest in its class. Enhancing the realism a life-like paint combination emulates the sand and brown hues found in the wild of this western-inspired 3-D target while the detailed vital section depicts the location of the heart lungs and liver at simulated angles. The ultra-durable 4-sided core is easily updated with replaceable vitals available separately.

  • Our Ball Loaded Index Point or BLIP for short is a feature found on all our lidded pouches and select plate carriers like the Trauma Kit NOW!. BLIP was born in the freezing rain on a Blackwater range. It was there we realized that when you cant feel your fingers its very difficult to get a grasp on a flat piece of webbing and distinguish a pull tab. The ball doesnt rely on friction; the bones in your fingers positively engage it. BLIPs form is both easy to pull and impossible to miss.

Web Item Name: Blue Force Gear The Shear Hammock Tourniquet Hammock Black
Web Item Description:
The Tourniquet Hammock is the quick and easy way to carry a CAT or SOF-T or RATS Tourniquet off of an existing belt or MOLLE mounted pouch that takes up no more additional mounting space and protects the tourniquet from the environment.  

With the Tourniquet Hammock you can keep your tourniquet readily accessible right below your Micro Trauma Kit with no extra mounting space needed.  As an added benefit the Tourniquet Hammock keeps the tourniquet better protected against damaging UV rays weather and dirt and debris than having a TQ simply rubber banded to your gear. 

The Tourniquet Hammock can be mounted to either the MOLLE or belt mounted Micro TKN or any other MOLLE pouch with a 3 column MOLLE foot print such as the Trauma Kit NOW! Vertical Utility Pouch and many others. Simply slide MOLLE straps through the slots on the Hammock towards the final installation point so that it hangs down or put the Hammock on first for it to ‘hang’ at the top.

Simply slide MOLLE straps through the slots on the Hammock towards the final installation point so that it hangs down or put the Hammock on first for it to ‘hang’ at the top.

Web Item Name: Muddy Pro Series 1075 Backpack Mossy Oak Bottomland
Web Item Description:
Regardless of where you hunt or how you hunt kick this season off with a hauls-it-all pack from Muddy’s newest lineup: The Pro Series. The smallest of six feature-loaded packs in our new hunt pack family the Pro 1075 Pack is the ideal minimalist day pack for hunters of every kind. It boasts 1075 cubic inches (equivalent to 17 liters) of storage space in a sleek and streamlined poly brush construction that not only stands up to repeated use with ease but minimizes noise while you hike crawl and stalk through all manner of environments as well. With one main storage compartment three front pockets and one kangaroo pocket with side compression straps it offers ample room for stowing all the gear and accessories you require for a day afield in a true minimalist design. And thanks to the pack’s padded shoulder straps adjustable sternum strap and cushioned adjustable waistbelt rest assured you’ll be met with plenty of support to see you through every haul. Topping off this hunting day pack is Mossy Oak’s trademark Bottomlands camouflage pattern which keeps your setup under wraps so you go undetected. What more could a hunter ask for?

FEATURES

  • The sleek design boasts 1075 cubic inches (17 liters) of storage space for hauling all your must-haves
  • Main storage compartment with three front pockets for keeping gear organized
  • Bonus kangaroo pocket with compression straps to lash your load down tight

Web Item Name: Muddy Pro Series Lumbar 500 Pack Mossy Oak Bottomland
Web Item Description:
When it comes to packs creating one that meets the unique demands of mobile hunters is a challenge all its own—one the entire Muddy team has been committed to tackling. And with the release of their newest lineup of hauls-it-all hunting backpacks the all-encompassing Pro Series they’ve made it happen in a big way. Introducing the Pro Lumbar 500 Pack a minimalistic 500-cubic-inch (8-liter) backpack that delivers all the storage space mobile hunters require without the extra weight and bulk that holds them back. Complete with a large main compartment and zipperless lid design as well as a front pocket and two waistbelt pockets with silent zippers this pack ensures simple silent access to must-have gear and accessories while allowing hunters to remain hands-free in the meantime. The pack’s durable poly brush fabric construction is outfitted in the original Mossy Oak Bottomlands camouflage and includes a two-piece adjustable waistbelt for a sure supportive fit that stands up to long days of spent spotting and stalking.

  • Two-piece adjustable waistbelt with two silent-zippered pockets
  • 100% poly brush material is soft durable and quiet material
  • Silent yet durable polyester brushed fabric construction in Mossy Oak Bottomlands camo

Item Name: STEALTH CAM DECEPTOR CELLULAR 40MP DUAL NETWORK CRACKED MUD CAMO
Web Item Name: StealthCam Deceptor No-Glo Cellular Trail Camera 40 MP Grey
Web Item Description:
Stealth Cam further refines the cellular camera segment with the introduction of the all-new Deceptor No-Glo cellular camera. With the new Stealth Cam Command Pro app you can keep in touch with the Deceptor No-Glo via your mobile device—anytime anywhere and our new ON DEMAND function allows you to send a command to the camera and capture photos and video of your hunting area in real time with the push of a button. Cellular reception can be problematic in remote areas and our new Automatic Network Coverage feature chooses the strongest Verizon or AT&T cell signal to make sure you have uninterrupted communication to your mobile device. You can now share your Deceptor No-Glo camera with other Stealth Cam Command Pro App users. Discover the functionality of sharing cameras and hunting intel with lease buddies family or friends or easily share individual images with your friends via text messages emails or popular social media platforms.

This camera leaves nothing on the table in regard to imaging and capture performance. The Deceptor No-Glo records sharp and detailed still images up to 40MP and takes high-resolution QHD 1440P video with audio. A 36-piece 940nm No-Glo LED array offers an invisible detection and flash range out to 80 feet. Coupled with a lightning-fast 0.3-second trigger speed and a selectable 5-second to 180-second recovery timeout the Deceptor No-Glo ensures you’ll never miss the action.

  • On Demand: Photo and Video
  • Camera Sharing: Via Command Pro App

Web Item Name: StealthCam Solar Power Panel 3000 Mah 10ft Insulated Metal Cable USB Port
Web Item Description:
Introducing the easiest way to keep all of your cellular trail cams charged while keeping your own boots off prime hunting ground - with the Sol-Pak solar battery pack from StealthCam.

Available with 3000mah and 5000mah lithium Ion batteries these amorphous solar panels rely on renewable energy not boxes of traditional batteries that cost a fortune and fizzle out at the most inopportune times.

The adjustable T-swivel brackets can be positioned to blend seamlessly into their surroundings while also easily gathering enough light to power your gear through back 2 back days of low-light conditions. Durable weather-resistant ABS housing stands up to wind rain and adverse weather.

Panels can be used individually or strung together for loads of additional power and are compatible with any camera that has an external 12-volt DC jack. Plus the convenient led battery indicator lets you know at a glance how much life is left. Integrated USB charging port and cable lock pass - through slots ensure setup with the adjustable nylon camera strap is swift and simple - no tools required.

Web Item Name: Stealth Cam Wildview 14 Infrared Flash Trail Camera
Web Item Description:
The Stealth Cam Wildview 14 Trail Camera stands out as a top-tier choice for wildlife enthusiasts hunters and nature photographers. This advanced trail camera offers a 14-megapixel resolution ensuring that every image and video captured is of exceptional clarity and detail even in the most challenging outdoor environments.

Equipped with infrared night vision technology the Wildview 14 excels in low-light conditions capturing the nocturnal activities of wildlife without disturbing them. The camera's motion-activated sensors trigger the camera to start recording as soon as movement is detected ensuring that you never miss a moment.

Durability is a key feature of this trail camera. It's built to withstand harsh weather conditions making it perfect for long-term deployment in the wild. The camera's compact and discreet design allows it to blend seamlessly into its surroundings providing uninterrupted wildlife observation.

The Wildview 14 is user-friendly with intuitive settings that make it easy to set up and operate. It offers various customizable options such as multi-shot modes time-lapse and video recording allowing you to tailor the camera's operation to your specific needs.

In summary the Stealth Cam Wildview 14 Trail Camera is a reliable high-performance device that brings you closer to nature. Whether you're tracking game monitoring wildlife or indulging in nature photography this trail camera is an indispensable tool. Its combination of high-quality imaging robust construction and ease of use make it an excellent choice for anyone looking to explore and document the natural world.

  • 14MP High-Resolution Imaging: Captures detailed wildlife photos and videos.
  • Infrared Night Vision: Excellent performance in low-light conditions.
  • Durable and Weatherproof: Ideal for long-term outdoor use.
  • Motion-Activated Sensors: Ensures no moment is missed.
  • User-Friendly Operation: Easy setup with customizable features.

The Stealthcam Wildview WV14 Trail Camera is the perfect camera for scouting your next hunting spot. The crystal clear 14 MP images and videos will let you see everything. The 0.7-second trigger speed will capture whatever is happening in front of it almost instantaneously.

  • 60 ft Detection & IR Range
  • Video recording options: 5/10/15 seconds
  • Burst Mode 1-3 images per triggering
  • 5-120 second recovery time out

  • Integrated Python lock latch
  • Crystal clear images and video
  • Quick set programming
  • 18 IR emitters
  • Burst mode
  • 5-60 second recovery time
  • Integrated python latch
  • Runs on 8AA batteries (Not Included)
  • Time/Date/Moon Phase image stamp

Web Item Name: Wildgame Innovations Terra Cellular Trail Camera 16MP AT&T
Web Item Description: Thanks to Wildgame Innovations’ Terra Cell 16-Megapixel Cellular Trail Camera you can keep a close eye on the farthest reaches of your property without fear of messing up established patterns of game animals residing there. Twenty-one 850nm LEDs pair with a whopping 80-ft. detection and flash range and rapid 0.7-second trigger speed to capture even the most fleeting appearances. Plus it automatically uploads organizes and analyzes captured photos using the Artificial Intelligence Management (AIM) System of Wildgame Innovations’ HuntSmart App providing information detailed out by species geolocation custom descriptions and much more. Setup is done  via QR code so you’re ready to accept the 16:9 ratio images on your phone or computer almost immediately. Powered by 8 AA Batteries (not included) or 12-volt DC jack compatible with solar power panels (not included).  Adjustable tree strap included. Cable-lock ready latch (security accessories not included) helps deter theft.

Item Name: Honeywell Safety Single Pack - Face Mask Gloves & Cleansing Wipes
Web Item Name: Howard Leight Safety Single Pack PPE Kit Face Mask Gloves & Cleansing Wipes
Web Item Description:
Enhance peace of mind for yourself and those around you with the Honeywell Safety Pack. This Honeywell PPE Kit is available in a resealable pouch that allows for convenient on the go access. Keep Honeywell Personal Protective Equipment in your car purse work bag backpack at the home for guests or anywhere else you’ll need them. Having the right equipment and solutions allows us to adapt to our new normal ensuring that we’re on the correct path to returning to work returning to life and reshaping the future as we know it – together.

Comfortable Fit

A comfortable face mask is less likely to be removed or adjusted during wear. These 3-ply face masks are lightweight for comfort during extended wear and pleated for easy expansion to fit most adult face sizes.

Surface Contact Avoidance

You can avoid directly touching surfaces and handling objects outside the home with non-sterile gloves. These gloves offer excellent versatility for performing everyday tasks. They're lightweight comfortable and latex-free.

Easy Surface Cleaning

Cleaning wipes offer a convenient solution for wiping down frequently touched out-of-home surfaces. These can include office door handles smart phones and your car's steering wheel.

Resealable Pouch

Avoid exposing your PPE to keys cash and coins when carrying it loosely on your person. The safety pack comes in a secure resealable pouch. This allows you to keep all of your PPE items organized and separated from your other belongings providing easy access when you need it.

Convenient Storage

The compact size of the Honeywell Safety Pack allows for convenient carrying and storage almost anywhere. If you're out walking the pouch easily fits into a purse handbag or backpack. You can also store it in a glove compartment or center console when driving.

  • This kit comes in an easy-to-open resealable pouch for your convenient access to the contents.
  • PPE safety pack contains: (1) face mask (1) pair of non-latex non-sterile gloves and (2) cleaning wipes.
  • Face Mask: 3 ply pleated lightweight material.
  • Gloves: Non-latex non-sterile. One size fits most adults.
  • Cleaning Wipes: % Alcohol > 60% Ethanol.
  • Safety Packs assembled in the U.S. with U.S. and imported components.

The SOF Tourniquet by TacMed Solutions sets the benchmark for pre-hospital tourniquets. Web Item Name: Tactacam Reveal Battery Belt

The Tactacam REVEAL Battery Belt is built for the long haul. With up to 3x the capacity of a standard lithium battery pack it’s made for extended deployments and high-demand setups. Item Name: LEM Products Maxvac 500 w/Bag Holder & Cutter
Web Item Name: LEM Products MaxVac 500 Vacuum Sealer w/Bag Holder & Cutter
Web Item Description:
The LEM Products MaxVac 500 Vacuum Sealer is a game-changer for those who take food preservation seriously. Designed for both avid hunters and culinary enthusiasts this commercial-grade vacuum sealer not only enhances the shelf life of your food but also ensures that flavors are locked in making it perfect for meal preps and sous vide cooking. With its robust construction the MaxVac 500 stands out for its reliability and efficiency in sealing a wide variety of foods from game meats to vegetables and beyond.

Equipped with a convenient bag holder and cutter this vacuum sealer simplifies the process of preparing bags for sealing saving time and reducing waste. The integrated bag cutter ensures clean customized bag sizes while the holder keeps rolls secure during operation. This feature-packed model is engineered to handle continuous sealing with a capability to seal up to 250 times without stopping making it ideal for bulk processing.

Whether preserving the bounty of your latest hunting trip or preparing ingredients for the week ahead the MaxVac 500 provides a professional-level sealing that is accessible for home use. Its user-friendly interface and durable design make it a valuable addition to any kitchen or processing setup ensuring that your foods stay fresh longer.

  • Commercial-Grade Performance: Designed for continuous use with up to 250 consecutive seals.
  • Integrated Bag Holder & Cutter: Simplifies bag preparation for efficient sealing.
  • Durable Construction: Built to last perfect for heavy-duty home or commercial use.
  • Versatile Sealing Capabilities: Ideal for a wide range of foods including meats vegetables and more.
  • User-Friendly Design: Easy to operate making professional vacuum sealing accessible at home.
  • Powerful and Easy-to-Use: The powerful pump and 14" x 1/4" seal bar will extract the air seal it tight and extend the freshness and freezer life of your favorite foods.
  • One Handed Locking Lid: With the 1-handed locking mechanism the other hand is free to hold the bag making it easy for you to lock in freshness and flavor with the flick of a switch.
  • Durable Construction: Aluminum construction means this unit is built to last and will blend in well with other kitchen appliances.
  • 5 Hours of Continuous Use: A built-in continuous run cooling fan on the LEM MaxVac® 500 allows for 5 consecutive hours of use and can do 500+ seals without stopping or cooling down.
  • Customizable Bag Size: Includes a roll material holder and cutter to customize your bag size. Includes 8" x 25' roll of bag material. Material holder and cutter can be removed for standalone use. will be visible when delivered.

 

Specifications:

  • Unprecedented 2 year warranty
  • Aluminum housing with one-hand locking lid
  • Rated for 5 hours and 500 consecutive seals
  • Circuit breaker for unit protection
  • Built-in cooling fan
  • Bag material holder and cutter
  • Auto mode vacuums and seals
  • Accessory port for storage containers
  • Cord length is 6' a minimum of 14 gauge is required when using an extension cord.
  • Extra large spill trough
  • 1/4" heat strip accommodates 14" wide bags
  • Includes bag material holder/cutter and one 8" x 25' roll of vacuum bag material
  • ETL-certified

By utilizing the integrated recoil-reduction sling shooters are able to relax and shoot more comfortably knowing that less recoil from the gun is going to be felt. The recoil reduction sling does not have to be used with lighter calibers rifles.

Item Name: MTM SPORTSMEN'S RUMP RESTER - GRD SEAT W/CARRYING STRAP FOREST GREEN
Web Item Name: MTM Sportsman's Rump Rester Ground Hunting Set Forest Green

Sitting still so the turkeys won't see you is no longer a challenge. Due to its special contour The Sportsmen's Rump Rester Turkey Hunting Seat provides a comfortable shooting position and can be used in either direction depending on the slope of the ground. Item Name: Primos Tall Timber Gabriel Wood Grain Sgl Sided w/Thumb Holes Clam E/F
Web Item Name: Primos Tall Timber Gabriel Turkey Call Box Call
Web Item Description:
The Tall Timber Gabriel is our Premium Box Call which features double thumbholes on the box to allow easy and perfect clucks and cuts. The name is derived from a book written by Will’s good friend Charles Whittington. Mr. Whittington wrote about his Turkey Hunting exploits in 1971 in a book entitled Tall Timber Gabriels.  He affectionately called a gobbler Old Gabriel after an angel.  Hence Tall Timber Gabriels because gobblers sing each spring from their tall timber perch sending out their love song for all to hear.

We have put all that we know and cherish about the box call as an instrument into this call: the choice of woods the curves of the striking surfaces the shape and cutouts of the sideboards as well as the finish to give you the finest instrument in reproducing the sounds that Old Gabriel so badly wants to hear.

Features:

  • Dual Thumbhole Positions For Clucks & Cuts
  • Premium Sapele & Purple Heart Wood
  • Laser Engraved
  • Hand Tuned

Web Item Name: Primos Trigger STick Apex Carbon Fiber with Tripod Black
Web Item Description:
More hunters are hunting more remotely than ever before. That means shot steadiness on tough terrain is more critical than ever before. Enter the Trigger Stick Apex™. Its super-strong yet lightweight carbon fiber wrapped aluminum legs deploy fast and adjust on the fly to even the trickiest terrain with a squeeze of the trigger. The rock-solid Apex-Frame® design allows quick adjustment and smooth panning to keep heavier rifles on-target and rock-solid from low sitting positions to nearly 6-foot-high standing positions. Its rugged construction supports a massive 50lb load capacity that would crush other shooting mounts. And the removable mounting plate makes switching from spotting scope to gun yoke quick and easy in the field. For great shots in the toughest conditions Trigger Stick Apex gets your there.

  • Securely mount firearm crossbow optics or camera
  • One-hand adjustments
  • Includes gun clamp
  • Removable mounting plate
  • Weighs 7 lbs
  • 62” max height
  • 28” folded height

Web Item Name: Primos Killer B Turkey Decoy
Web Item Description:
Last spring we sent B-Mobile™ to a plastic surgeon and what came back was Killer B™. We updated the paint scheme to bring out more iridescent colors in the body and more red in his head. We gave him glass eyes from a taxidermist that make him so realistic that it looks like he is staring at you. We created a tail fan that can move from full strut to ¾ strut to lying flat. We even updated his posture to make him look more like a strutting gobbler.

Killer B™ is made from the same proprietary formula that we have all come to love with B-Mobile™. You can also roll up Killer B™ for easy carry in your vest. This is the most realistic decoy on the market and the one you will find in all of the Primos Video Team members’ vests when they go into the field. B-Mobile™ brought them in close. Killer B™ will have them strutting in your lap….

Web Item Name: Primos Bottleneck Deer Grunt Call
Web Item Description:
Primos Bottleneck Deer Grunt Call – Compact Realistic Buck Call for Whitetail Hunting

The Primos Bottleneck Deer Grunt Call is built for hunters who want to sound like the real thing when calling in whitetail bucks. Designed with a soft flexible bottleneck shape this call automatically creates the perfect back pressure for authentic deer vocalizations. Whether you’re producing mid-tone grunts to lure curious bucks or powerful ROARs during the rut the Bottleneck Deer Grunt lets you “Speak the Language” with confidence.

Its compact single-reed design makes it easy to carry in the field while the all-rubber construction keeps it quiet durable and weather-resistant. The included lanyard ensures your grunt call is always ready when a trophy buck steps into range. Ideal for pre-rut peak rut and post-rut whitetail hunting.

Features:

  • Premium single-reed deer grunt call for whitetail hunting
  • Produces realistic mid-tone buck grunts and aggressive ROARs
  • Flexible bottleneck design for perfect back pressure and natural sound
  • Soft all-rubber construction for quiet carry and all-weather performance
  • Compact size fits easily in your pocket or pack
  • Includes lanyard for quick easy access in the field
  • Perfect for rut hunting and year-round deer calling practice

Item Name: Browning Light Highnoon Power Pro CMPT 1250 Max Lumens
Web Item Name: Browning High Noon Power Pro Compact Spotlight 1250 Max Lumens - Coyote Tan
Web Item Description:
Long distance beam in a compact spotlight. With 1250 lumens and multiple lighting modes reaching 680 yards. Includes rechargeable li-ion battery that can be charged or continuously powered by USB 110V AC or 12V DC. Includes Power Bank feature waterproof submersible and floats.

Illuminating technology. While waterfowl hunters are searching for the perfect hole to set up their dozens of decoys the High Noon Power Pro Compact’s waterproof design provides 680 yards of light to help find that location. With the Power Bank feature hunters can charge other USB devices from the internal battery.

The High Noon Power Pro Compact is a feature rich spotlight that has one additional feature that is not common to other rechargeable hand helds it can be used continuously without recharging with 110V AC or 12V DC power using the included USB cable and vehicle adaptor or with a USB wall adaptor (not included). The integrated low battery indicator glows red when charging green when fully charged and amber when battery has 20% or less capacity remaining.

The Power Pro Compact has high low and a flashing mode for signaling. High mode offers 1250 lumens and reaches out to 680 yards. On the low setting the light will operate for up to 36 hours. The high-impact polymer housing and rubber lens ring protects against drops. The spotlight is also ready for wet weather – it's waterproof submersible and even floats. A folding stand with multiple positions offers hands-free use.

Features

  • 3000 mAh USB rechargeable li-ion battery can be charged or continuously powered by USB 110V AC or 12V DC using the included cable and vehicle adaptor or USB wall adaptor (not included)
  • High low and flashing modes
  • Power Bani
  • Low battery indicator glows red when charging green when fully charged and amber when battery has 20% or less capacity remaining
  • Includes 6-1/2 micro USB charging cable 12V input/5V-2.4A output vehicle adaptor and lanyard

Web Item Name: Centerpoint Dagger 405 Crossbow 4x32 illum Scope / Whisper Silencing & Accessories Package
Web Item Description:
The Dagger 405 takes the evolution of performance even further for CenterPoint. Complete with an adjustable butt pad the Dagger 405 crossbow proves to be an ergonomic fit for hunters and shooters. The Centerpoint Dagger 405 Crossbow is designed for hunters who demand precision and power in their equipment. Between the ripping speeds of this crossbow’s 405 fps and features including the Whisper Silencing System the game won’t know what’s coming.

The whisper silent Dagger 405 is outfitted with the best stealth system on the market. This crossbow offers exceptional accuracy thanks to its high-speed design and reliable energy transfer system. CenterPoint Archery’s Whisper Silencing System technology takes the major points of vibration and stops it in its tracks. From limb dampeners to string silencers this stealth black crossbow has the tech to prevent your target from reacting until it’s too late. Its hunter-designed frame allows you to comfortably maneuver around rugged terrain and rest the bow in perfect line with your sight and the target.

This CenterPoint package features include:

  • Whisper Silencing SystemIncludes string stops limb dampeners and string silencers for superior stealth and stability
  • 15" Axle-to-axle Fully CockedClassic hunter-designed compound frame for performance and easy transport
  • CNC Machined Aluminum Rail and Cam SystemFor smooth firing and repeatable shot placement
  • Ball Bearing Retention SpringUnique retention spring design for consistent and repeatable arrow tension that does not interfere with the cocking cycle
  • 220 lb. Draw WeightDelivers the energy needed for the crossbow’s incredible 405 fps speeds
  • Full Accessory Package: 4x32 illuminated scope parallel quiver rope cocker rail lube and (3) 20" .003 arrows

The Centerpoint crossbow Dagger 405 is an excellent choice for those seeking a high-performance hunting tool that combines power accuracy and stealth.

Web Item Name: Ravin R10 Crossbow 400 FPS 12 lb Draw XK7 Camo
Web Item Description:
A go-to for both highly experienced hunters & shooters and beginners the R10 is a classic Ravin model with excellent multi-usage capabilities. Although slim and light it delivers precise accuracy with breathtaking arrow speeds of over 400 FPS – perfect for hanging out in a tree stand or ground blind.

All Ravin XK7 crossbows except those in Sniper packages come with an illuminated scope that integrates an all new speed lock. This locking ring gives hunters confidence that their scope remains dialed in when it’s time to pull the trigger.

Features:

  • 20-100 yard reticles
  • Red & green illumination
  • Fog shock recoil and waterproof
  • Fully coated lenses
  • Speed Lock feature lets you lock-in your fps adjustment for next-level confidence in your shot.

Web Item Name: Ravin R10 Crossbow with Helicoil Technology - Black
Web Item Description:
HELICOIL® TECHNOLOGY

The engine behind Ravin crossbows. This revolutionary technology has several industry changing advantages that all work together to create the most accurate crossbow ever designed. HeliCoil technology coils cables away from both the top and bottom of the cams in helical grooves keeping the cams perfectly balanced. This allows the cams to rotate an incredible 340 degrees while both cams remain perfectly level when drawing and shooting the crossbow. This revolutionary design creates an incredibly compact crossbow packed full of innovative features that produce rifle-like downrange accuracy.

VERSA-DRAW™ COCKING SYSTEM

One of the revolutionary design advantages provided by HeliCoil technology is the Versa-Draw Cocking System. Working in conjunction with the Trac-Trigger Firing System this ultra-compact fully integrated cocking mechanism is built into the sleek stock design. Featuring a minimal 12 pounds of cocking force the Versa-Draw Cocking System is ambidextrous and has the ability to cock and un-cock your Ravin crossbow. This unique Helicoil advantage provides an easy to use fully integrated cocking mechanism delivering unmatched accuracy with every shot.

TRAC-TRIGGER™ FIRING SYSTEM

A patented built-in trigger mechanism that slides forward on the rail and clasps directly to the precise center of the string every time the bow is drawn allowing for straight-line nock travel. This unique HeliCoil advantage creates a perfectly balanced draw for unmatched down range accuracy with every shot.

FRICTIONLESS™ FLIGHT SYSTEM

This patented technology allows the arrow and string to free float above the rail eliminating friction for consistent accuracy and increased string and cable life. This unique HeliCoil advantage delivers astounding target accuracy with every shot.

INCLUDES

  • Built-In Cocking Mechanism
  • Anti-Dry Fire/Auto Safety
  • Built-in Sling Mounts
  • Removable Draw Handle
  • Quiver/Mounting Bracket
  • 3 Ravin .003 Premium Arrows & Field Tips (400 Grain Total)
  • 100 Yard Illuminated Scope

This unique Helicoil advantage provides an easy to use fully integrated cocking mechanism delivering unmatched accuracy with every shot.

TRAC-TRIGGER™ FIRING SYSTEM

A patented built-in trigger mechanism that slides forward on the rail and clasps directly to the precise center of the string every time the bow is drawn allowing for straight-line nock travel. This unique HeliCoil advantage creates a perfectly balanced draw for unmatched down range accuracy with every shot.

FRICTIONLESS™ FLIGHT SYSTEM

This patented technology allows the arrow and string to free float above the rail eliminating friction for consistent accuracy and increased string and cable life. This unique HeliCoil advantage delivers astounding target accuracy with every shot.

Web Item Name: Ravin R26X Crossbow
Web Item Description:
Like all Ravin crossbows the R26X delivers apex accuracy supreme power and unrivaled technology. What makes it distinct is its close-quarters maneuverability and light and lean form factor. As a bullpup-style bow the R26X is perfect for those who want to maintain equal parts agility and accuracy.

At just 26” long and 5.75” wide axle-to-axle cocked the Ravin R26X is extremely compact. Combined with its silent cocking your stealth and maneuverability get even more of the spotlight.

At 6.5 lbs the R26X is light and lean enough for saddle hunters and those with smaller frames.

The R26X integrates advanced Ravin technology that makes it one of the most accurate 400 fps crossbows on the planet. HeliCoil technology rotates each cam up to 340º while keeping them perfectly balanced. The Versa-Draw Cocking System and Trac-Trigger Firing System combine to ensure straight-line nock travel–a lethally silent combination.

R26X models are also available in XK7 camo with 100-Yard Illuminated Speed Lock Scope

Web Item Name: Ravin LR Long Range Crossbow Tan
Web Item Description:
The Ravin LR redefines long-range crossbow accuracy and performance. Inspired by modern day long-range rifles it delivers power precision and incredible accuracy. Featuring a longer profile for enhanced balance and reduced recoil this crossbow is built for downrange accuracy at distances up to 135 yards. Shooting at 450 FPS with 180 foot-pounds of kinetic energy the LR offers consistent performance with a silent cocking system and adjustable cheek comb and stock for a custom fit.

The full-length Picatinny rail supports additional accessories like the included 1-8x24 adjustable-turret scope. Fully assembled and hunt-ready the LR also comes with a scope level three-arrow quiver draw handle three .001 premium arrows and Ravin’s premium arrow rest.

Web Item Name: Umarex DSX45 Spring BB Handgun .177 Cal
Web Item Description:
The Umarex DSX45 BB Gun is designed for casual shooting and beginner training and resembles the modern 2011-style handgun with a flared mag well. This airgun is a perfect choice for those new to the sport of airgun shooting offering a blend of safety simplicity and fun. It's modeled to provide a feel similar to traditional handguns making it an excellent tool for basic handgun training and target practice. The operation of the DSX45 involves easy-to-use mechanisms that are perfect for beginners. The spring action of the slide provides a straightforward shooting experience without the need for CO2 cartridges. It’s crafted from durable polymers so it is lightweight yet robust making it easy to handle for users of many ages. The DSX45 uses standard .177 caliber steel BBs which are readily available and affordable making it convenient for regular use. With a large 200-round capacity reservoir in the drop-free magazine you can enjoy extended shooting sessions without the need to frequently reload. It features a 240 feet per second velocity blade and ramp front sight and a fixed open rear sight for basic targeting and is equipped with a manual trigger block safety ensuring safe handling especially for young or inexperienced shooters. The smooth bore barrel is designed for shooting BBs with precision at short ranges and it offers a respectable muzzle velocity suitable for target practice and plinking providing a realistic shooting experience. To load the magazine of the Umarex DSX45 release the mag from the pistol grip. Open the loading door on the bottom of the magazine and pour in up to 200 steel BBs. Close the door and pull the tab located right by the magazine’s loading door outward from the magazine. Pull it all the way out until it stops. Turn the magazine and shake it gently to allow 13 BBs to fall from the reservoir into the magazine tube then reinsert the mag into the grip. Be sure you’re wearing safety glasses to protect your eyes and always keep it pointed in a safe direction. Grip the pistol acquire your airgun target pull back on the slide until it stops then let it go forward to charge the pistol then put the pistol on fire and send it! Overall the Umarex DSX45 BB Pistol is an excellent choice for those looking to get started in airgun shooting or for those looking to add to their airgun collection. It provides an enjoyable introduction to shooting sports making it ideal for backyard plinking and basic target practice.

  • Spring air powered pistol
  • Drop free magazine with 200 round reservoir
  • 13 shot rapid load magazine
  • 240 FPS Pull and release slide
  • Grip Texturing Picatinny-style rail

Web Item Name: Umarex Bowfishing Airjavelin FishR PCP
Web Item Description: Are you ready to bring the power of air to your bowfishing waters? Umarex's AirJavelin FishR takes bowstring out of bowfishing with the power of precisely regulated air pressure. The AirJavelin FishR is powered by high-pressure air stored in an on-board tank at 4500 psi. The pressure is regulated to 800 psi which in turn launches a solid fiberglass arrow at 100 fps. Shoot the FishR intuitively or attach an optic that you can tune for your preferred shooting depth or technique. The AirJavelin FishR features a reel mount full-length top Picatinny Rail and stainless and corrosion resistant parts for long life in harsh/salt environments. Expect to get over 65 shots per fill of the 155cc tank.

Shoot the FishR intuitively or attach an optic that you can tune for your preferred shooting depth or technique. The AirJavelin FishR features a reel mount full-length top Picatinny Rail and stainless and corrosion resistant parts for long life in harsh/salt environments. Expect to get over 65 shots per fill of the 155cc tank.

Item Name: UMAREX AIRJAVELIN CO2 POWERED AIR ARCHERY AIRGUN RIFLE
Web Item Name: Umarex AirJavelin Co2 Powered Air Archery Airgun Rifle
Web Item Description:
The Umarex AirJavelin is a new way to shoot arrows. Powered by CO2 the Umarex Air Javelin launches a 170-grain air bolt at 300 fps. The AirJavelin takes airpower into a new direction with 34-foot pounds of energy delivered via Straight Flight Technology arrows. Shooters can line up the target with the installed open sights or zero in a dot sight or scope for pin-point arrow placement. The AirJavelin has a full-length Picatinny rail on the top along with a short section below the barrel. Both sides of the AirJavelin's stock are also equipped with M-LOK slots. The AirJavelin accepts 88-gram CO2 tanks and will launch dozens of arrows downrange on a single tank. The Umarex 2x12g CO2 adapter (not included) will also install on the AirJavelin handy for shorter shooting sessions. Lightweight and versatile the Umarex AirJavelin is more than a new way to shoot arrows it is a great way to open up archery fun for the whole family.

Use ONLY Umarex AirJavelin Arrows with the AirJavelin arrow gun. Use of other arrows can cause serious injury or even death. AirJavelin arrows are engineered for strength sufficient to handle extremely high CO2 pressure. Arrows for bows and crossbows are not strong enough to withstand the high CO2 pressure and can explode when pressurized. This can cause serious injury to the shooter and bystanders.

Item Name: THOMPSON PROHUNTER FS KATAHDIN 209X50 FIRESTICK M/L 20'' SST/FLEXTECH STOCK
Web Item Name: Thompson Center Encore Prohunter FS Katahdin Muzzleloader 209x50 Firestick M/l 20'' SST/FlexTech Stock
Web Item Description:
With the great looks quality and accuracy of the ever popular Thompson Center Encore ProHunter™ this muzzleloader combines the advanced features of the ProHunter rifle with Thompson Center’s solid reputation for durability and performance in the field. The T/C Pro Hunter FS is a Firestick ignition variation of the ProHunter XT muzzleloader. This model ships with a .50 caliber 20-inch muzzleloader barrel equipped from the factory.

This muzzleloader utilizes the Federal® FireStick™ system which takes the guesswork out of muzzleloading and increases safety and simplicity. The ProHunter FS muzzleloader is a great gun for beginners and experienced shooters alike. This .50 caliber muzzleloader is one of the easiest to load requires the least equipment and accessories and is incredibly accurate. 

The Federal™ FireStick is a vital component to this groundbreaking new muzzleloader. The FireStick is a plastic capsule that holds pre-measured powder charges. The ability to have identical charges on every shot allows for a more consistent velocity spread which increases accuracy and dependability. Since the FireSticks are only used once there is no real cleaning involved in the breech area which speeds up reloading as well. This technology reduces the need for many common accessories which makes it much easier for beginners to get into the sport. Powder measures powder flasks nipple picks speed loaders cappers parts soakers and granular or pelletized powders are not needed with this muzzleloader which can save hunters lots of money when they are first getting into muzzleloading. With this new muzzleloader all you’ll need to carry in the field are a couple primers bullets FireSticks and a bullet starter! 

Other notable features include the muzzleloader’s improved handling and recoil reduction system made possible by the FlexTech™ stock and forend. Inside the FlexTech stock are four Energy Burners™ along with the recoil pad allowing the stock to compress slightly when fired helping to reduce felt recoil by forty-two percent. Additionally the ProHunter FS muzzleloader does not require a breech plug due to the FireStick ignition.

The ProHunter FS™ muzzleloader is drilled and tapped for scope mounts. It comes standard with Williams™ fiber optic sights along with a Swing Hammer® that can be conveniently positioned toward either side of the frame enabling easier access to the hammer under mounted scopes. Weighing in at just 7 pounds the ProHunter FS features a 14-inch length of pull crisp trigger and deadly accuracy.

To protect the muzzleloader against inclement weather Thompson Center has added its tough-as-nails finish WeatherShield®. When applied to the barrel receiver and other rifle critical parts the WeatherShield coating adds an extra level of protection against corrosion while extending the durability and life of the muzzleloader.

FFL Required.

The ProHunter FS muzzleloader is a great gun for beginners and experienced shooters alike. This .50 caliber muzzleloader is one of the easiest to load requires the least equipment and accessories and is incredibly accurate. 

The Federal™ FireStick is a vital component to this groundbreaking new muzzleloader. The FireStick is a plastic capsule that holds pre-measured powder charges. The ability to have identical charges on every shot allows for a more consistent velocity spread which increases accuracy and dependability. Since the FireSticks are only used once there is no real cleaning involved in the breech area which speeds up reloading as well. This technology reduces the need for many common accessories which makes it much easier for beginners to get into the sport. Powder measures powder flasks nipple picks speed loaders cappers parts soakers and granular or pelletized powders are not needed with this muzzleloader which can save hunters lots of money when they are first getting into muzzleloading. With this new muzzleloader all you’ll need to carry in the field are a couple primers bullets FireSticks and a bullet starter! 

Other notable features include the muzzleloader’s improved handling and recoil reduction system made possible by the FlexTech™ stock and forend. Inside the FlexTech stock are four Energy Burners™ along with the recoil pad allowing the stock to compress slightly when fired helping to reduce felt recoil by forty-two percent. Other features of the Stealth 450 include the innovative ACUslide cocking/de-cocking mechanism. This system allows the shooter to silently cock/un-cock the crossbow by cranking the ACUslide’s handle and the entire process can be paused at any time. In addition the Stealth 450 is equipped with the S1 Trigger a 2-stage zero-creep design with a roller sear system that provides a crisp consistent 3.5 lb pull.

Features

  • Scope Struts: The new Scope Struts connect the scope rail to the main body providing 80% increased strength which results in increased accuracy and added durability.
  • ACUslide Cocking and Decocking: An integrated ACUslide crank device allows the user to safely and silently cock and decock the crossbow without firing an arrow.
  • S1 Trigger: The 2-stage zero creep S1 trigger uses a roller sear system for a crisp trigger break allowing you to consistently break a clean shot.
  • Micro-trac Barrel: The crossbow rail on the TenPoint

Stealth 450 Specs

  • Length (w/o foot stirrup): 33″
  • Width (axle-to-axle uncocked): 6.5″
  • Power Stroke: 13″
  • Weight (w/o accessories): 7.5lbs.
  • Speed (400gr. Pro Elite Arrow): 450fps.
  • Speed (465gr. Evo-X Centerpunch Arrow): 430fps.

Web Item Name: TenPoint Siege 425 ACUslide RangeMaster 100 Scope Moss Green
Web Item Description:
Shooting 425 feet-per-second and measuring an ultra-compact 26.5″ inches short and 7.5″ narrow the supercharged Tenpoint Siege 425 delivers 100-yard nock-breaking accuracy.

Featuring a micro-footprint and low profile the Siege 425 is designed with the mobile hunter mind. Whether it’s a two-mile trek on public land or the need to adapt to deer patterns the Siege 425 gives you the freedom to pack your stand and kit and make that aggressive move for success.

Equipped with the best-in-class ACUslide™ (patented) for silent and safe de-cocking the Siege 425 received the full accuracy treatment as well thanks to Scope Struts and RangeMaster® 100 scope which combine to drive nock-breaking down-range accuracy.

Scope Struts provide a rock-solid foundation for optics and “bulletproof” in-the-field durability. The Siege 425 is paired with the ultra-compact 16″ EVO-X® CenterPunch™ 16 arrow which ensures your entire crossbow setup works well in the tightest of hunting situations.

Features & Benefits

  • Ultra-Compact Hunting System: Micro-footprint paired with a 16” arrow that takes up 20% less space in quiver and fits within the crossbow’s framework redefines crossbow maneuverability and performance when inches of clearance matter.
  • ACUslide (patented) Cocking & De-Cocking System: Provides silent cocking and safe de-cocking.
  • Scope Struts: Provide a rock-solid foundation for optics to deliver long-range accuracy and “bulletproof” in-the-field durability.
  • RangeMaster 100: Variable speed scope maximizes accuracy out to 100-yards and built for speeds up to 505 FPS.
  • Reverse-Draw Design: Generates more speed with less draw weight for a smoother shot and provides superior balance for increased accuracy.
  • S1™ Trigger: 2-stage zero-creep design features a roller sear system that sets the standard in high-performance crossbow accuracy.
  • Sentry Bowhanger: Easily hang your bow in the stand or protect your broadhead from dirt and grit in the ground blind.

Package Includes:

  • RangeMaster 100 Scope
  • ACUslide Cocking and De-Cocking System
  • 3 CenterPunch 16 Carbon Arrows
  • Integrated String Stop
  • Sentry Bowhanger
  • Quiver

Web Item Description:
Shooting 425 feet-per-second and measuring an ultra-compact 26.5″ inches short and 7.5″ narrow the supercharged Tenpoint Siege 425 delivers 100-yard nock-breaking accuracy.

Featuring a micro-footprint and low profile the Siege 425 is designed with the mobile hunter mind. Whether it’s a two-mile trek on public land or the need to adapt to deer patterns the Siege 425 gives you the freedom to pack your stand and kit and make that aggressive move for success.

Equipped with the best-in-class ACUslide™ (patented) for silent and safe de-cocking the Siege 425 received the full accuracy treatment as well thanks to Scope Struts and RangeMaster® 100 scope which combine to drive nock-breaking down-range accuracy.

Scope Struts provide a rock-solid foundation for optics and “bulletproof” in-the-field durability. The Siege 425 is paired with the ultra-compact 16″ EVO-X® CenterPunch™ 16 arrow which ensures your entire crossbow setup works well in the tightest of hunting situations.

Features & Benefits

  • Ultra-Compact Hunting System: Micro-footprint paired with a 16” arrow that takes up 20% less space in quiver and fits within the crossbow’s framework redefines crossbow maneuverability and performance when inches of clearance matter.
  • ACUslide (patented) Cocking & De-Cocking System: Provides silent cocking and safe de-cocking.
  • Scope Struts: Provide a rock-solid foundation for optics to deliver long-range accuracy and “bulletproof” in-the-field durability.
  • RangeMaster 100: Variable speed scope maximizes accuracy out to 100-yards and built for speeds up to 505 FPS.
  • Reverse-Draw Design: Generates more speed with less draw weight for a smoother shot and provides superior balance for increased accuracy.
  • S1™ Trigger: 2-stage zero-creep design features a roller sear system that sets the standard in high-performance crossbow accuracy.
  • Sentry Bowhanger: Easily hang your bow in the stand or protect your broadhead from dirt and grit in the ground blind.

Package Includes:

  • RangeMaster 100 Scope
  • ACUslide Cocking and De-Cocking System
  • 3 CenterPunch 16 Carbon Arrows
  • Integrated String Stop
  • Sentry Bowhanger

Item Name: Tenpoint TRX 26 ACUslide MAXX RangeMaster 100 Scope
Web Item Name: Tenpoint TRX 26 Compact Reverse-Draw Crossbow ACUslide MAXX RangeMaster 100 Scope Black
Web Item Description:
The Tenpoint TRX 26 is their lightest and narrowest reverse-draw crossbow ever. Shooting 460 FPS it is built with a micro-footprint and low profile at 26.5” short and 5.75” narrow – giving you the freedom and mobility to go further while packing a stand or the gear you need to be successful and giving you more shooting coverage by reducing the chance for cam or limb contact in the treestand or ground blind.

The TRX 26 is equipped with a TriggerTech Trigger ZERO-Trac Barrel™ and GUIDE-Lock™ Arrow Rest System that create the most secure consistent launch platform ever built for a crossbow.

The ACU-Lock™ Scope Bridge provides the ultimate foundation for scope stability and the ACUSlide MAXX™ provides silent and safe de-cocking.

Features & Benefits

  • 100-yard RangeMaster 100 Scope: Variable speed scope maximizes accuracy out to 100-yards and built for speeds up to 505 FPS.
  • Twin-Riser Technology: 41% lighter and 2x stiffer than traditional risers TRT is designed with symmetrical top and bottom plates that reduce riser flex noise and vibration – resulting in unmatched accuracy and greater long-term durability.
  • TriggerTech Precision Trigger: Zero-Creep trigger features Frictionless Release Technology (FRT) that “breaks like glass” to improve accuracy and precision.
  • AR-Style Ambidextrous Thumb Safety: Conveniently located safety allows you to keep both hands on the crossbow and eyes locked on your game.
  • ZERO-Trac Barrel & GUIDE-Lock Arrow Rest System: Rail-less design reduces weight while GUIDE-Lock Rest System fully captures the arrow for unprecedented down-range precision.
  • ACUslide MAXX (patented) Cocking & De-Cocking System: Provides silent cocking and safe de-cocking. Stronger smoother and easier to operate. Remove your hand at any point and the handle stops in place.
  • ACU-Lock Scope Bridge: 25x stronger than traditional scope rails to provide the ultimate foundation for scope stability and accuracy.
  • Reverse-Draw Design: Generates more speed with less draw weight for a smoother shot and provides superior balance for increased accuracy.

Package Includes:

  • 100-yard RangeMaster 100 Scope
  • ACUslide MAXX
  • 3 CenterPunch HPX Carbon Arrows
  • Integrated String Stop
  • Bow Hook
  • Quiver

Item Name: Phantom Decock ACUdraw De-Cock Pro-View 400 Scope
Web Item Name: TenPoint Phantom Decock Crossword ACUdraw De-Cock Pro-View 400 Scope
Web Item Description:
The Phantom De-Cock is an ultra-compact reverse-draw crossbow weighing just 7.4-pounds and measuring just 8.4-inches narrow and 28.5-inches short. Featuring the ACUdraw De-Cock system and a newly designed stock and barrel configuration the Phantom De-Cock delivers speeds up to 400 FPS with same-hole accuracy defining it as a highly accurate crossbow.

The reverse-draw platform delivers an incredible balance unmatched in traditional crossbow designs eliminating front-heaviness to allow for easy one-handed maneuvering effortless shouldering and reduced holding weight that benefits hunters of all upper body strengths. If you haven’t shouldered a reverse-draw bow it’s unlike any other style—it’s something you need to experience to truly appreciate how the exceptional balance makes every shot more controlled and comfortable.

Bringing reverse-draw performance to an unheard-of price point the Phantom De-Cock pairs our ACUdraw De-Cock system with a newly designed stock and bow assembly. This creates a ultra-narrow profile for TenPoint's reverse-draw crossbow delivering better value than ever for a high-performance value crossbow!

Features & Benefits

  • Reverse-Draw Design: Perfectly balanced reverse-draw design eliminates the front-heavy feel of crossbows for rock-steady offhand shots while delivering blistering speeds with a lower draw weight for quieter shots and less vibration.
  • ACUdraw De-Cock Cocking & De-Cocking System: While other de-cocking crossbows force you to “hang on to the crank handle for dear life” – the ACUdraw De-Cock delivers safe controlled de-cocking that anyone in the family can use with confidence ensuring you own a truly safe de-cocking crossbow.
  • D1 Trigger (Patented): 2- stage zero creep design featuring a DFP (Dry-Fire-Prohibitor) delivers a consistent crisp 3 ½ – pound pull.
  • 70-Yard Pro-View 400 Lighted Scope: Offers aimpoints out to 70-yards & features a lighted reticle for a cleaner view & greater down-range accuracy. (illuminated red or green)
  • Stock & Barrel Design: Features upgrades typically found at higher price points including a metal barrel that eliminates barrel flex and reduces friction for improved string life plus rubber touch points for added comfort on the stock cheek piece butt plate and pistol grip.
  • Superior Shooting Comfort: TenPoint optimized every ergonomic element—comb height length-of-pull grips—so these crossbows feel like natural body extensions for maximum accuracy.
  • Sentry Bowhanger: The Sentry Bowhanger offers easy hanging while keeping your broadhead out of the dirt when hunting from a blind.

  • ACUdraw De-Cock Silent Cocking and Safe De-Cocking System
  • Pro-View 400 Lighted Scope

Item Name: TX Ultra 29.5 ACUslide MAXX EVO-X Elite Scope
Web Item Name: Tenpoint TX Ultra 29.5 Crossbow ACUslide MAXX Moss with EVO-X Elite Scope
Web Item Description:
Measuring 29.5" short and 6.5" narrow the TX Ultra 29.5 shoots 460 FPS and features Twin-Riser Technology (TRT) a custom TriggerTech Trigger AR-Style Ambidextrous Thumb Safety and multiple precision-engineered accuracy advancements capable of 3" groups at 100-yards creating the most accurate crossbow in its class.

Every component is designed with sniper-like accuracy and category-leading reliability. NEW 8 MM Axles and X-Wide Limbs create a more stable repeatable and reliable shooting platform while the ACU-X Arrow with Snap-On Nock and upgraded custom string deliver devastating long-range accuracy.

At 29.5” in length the TX Ultra 29.5 provides added stability for long-range shooting situations.

Features & Benefits

  • Zero-Torsion Technology: 8MM Axles (175% stronger and 215% stiffer than standard axles) & X-Wide Limbs (20% wider and 120% stronger than standard limbs) combine to eliminate all torsional movement along the limb axis.
  • ACU-X Arrows with Snap-On Nock: Features a high-performance carbon shaft and a new precision spine-indexing manufacturing technique – placing the spine of the arrow in the exact configuration that has been tested and proven to perform best specifically for our rail-less forward draw crossbows delivering the ultimate in consistency and long-range accuracy out of this platform. The ACU-X Snap-On Nock delivers precision long-range accuracy while preserving string center serving life.
